sql.description: Certain Book: Topics and Occurrence Count
sql.query: select t.display_name_do_not_use name, t.tct_id id, count(o.topic_id) ocount from occurrences o  INNER JOIN locations l  ON o.location_id = l.tct_id INNER JOIN topics t  ON t.tct_id      = o.topic_id WHERE l.epub_id = 71 GROUP BY t.display_name_do_not_use ORDER BY ocount DESC
